rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真我又唔係話誇張到想啲人入黎講啲<br />\n嘩樓主真係好撚勁呀,樓主真係連登之光呢啲咁得人驚既野<br />\n但入黎見到個巴打咁努力,講句樓主真係有心,加油樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都叫幾好呀<br />\n好可惜,原來係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaead6d416062f4b1566d4ecd342bd0ff9cb106e","tid":384341,"uid":143693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好放棄<br />\n加油做好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}